               <p>J. Alcock. These Goods were lost out of my Shew-glass. I was sent for to Justice Deveil's, where I found 
               <persName id="t17330912-27-person223">
                  Ned 
                  Langford 
               <interp inst="t17330912-27-person223" type="surname" value="Langford"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17330912-27-person223" type="given" value="Ned"></interp>
