            , alias Nimble Jack, who said, he knew me very well, for that he and the Prisoners had stolen all these Things out of my Shop at <placeName id="t17330912-27-crimeloc136">Cripple-gate</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17330912-27-crimeloc136" type="placeName" value="Cripple-gate"></interp>
